    • StorageSettings

      public StorageSettings(boolean isInUse, String rootPath, int storageMaxSize, Collection<String> extensionBlacklist, Map<String,Integer> directoryMaxFileSize)
      Constructor for the StorageSettings object.
      Parameters:
      isInUse - Boolean variable that tells us if somebody is already logged in the storage.
      rootPath - Path to the root directory of the storage.
      storageMaxSize - Maximum size of the storage.
      extensionBlacklist - List of extensions that are forbidden in the storage.
      directoryMaxFileSize - Map of directories and their maximum file number limits.
